description: The path on which to base the contour text wrap.

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the object's bounding box.
properties.name: BOUNDING_BOX

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the specified Photoshop path. To specify the Photoshop path, see contour path name.
properties.name: PHOTOSHOP_PATH

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the edges of the image.
properties.name: DETECT_EDGES

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the edges of the specified alpha channel. To specify the alpha channel, see contour path name.
properties.name: ALPHA_CHANNEL

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the wrapped object's graphics frame.
properties.name: GRAPHIC_FRAME

properties.description: Sets the text wrap shape to the clipping path (if any) defined in Photoshop. Note: A path cannot be specified using this enumeration. To set the text wrap shape to a specific path, use the photoshop path contour options type enumeration value.
properties.name: SAME_AS_CLIPPING

name: ContourOptionsTypes
